## ğŸ› ï¸ Setup Instructions

> Preferably run the notebooks in Google Colab for hassle-free environment management.

### ğŸ” Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Priya-Rathor/generative-ai-nlp.git
cd generative-ai-nlp
````

### ğŸ“¦ Install Dependencies

You can install the required libraries locally using:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Or install them one-by-one inside Colab based on the notebook you're using.

---

## ğŸ” API Keys Required

Some notebooks require API access.

* **OpenAI**

  * Get your key from: [platform.openai.com](https://platform.openai.com/)
  * Use: `openai.api_key = "your_key"`

* **Hugging Face**

  * Create an account at [huggingface.co](https://huggingface.co/)
  * Use the key via `transformers` CLI or set in notebook

* **Weaviate**

  * Use Weaviate Cloud Service (WCS) or local Docker instance
  * Configure `.env` or inline keys

